channel.title: Oracle-Scape Looking for client and server developer
channel.description:
I have founded this server for about 5-6 months and i have been keeping this server running for at least 6 months but i did take a brake from it. But i am glad to announce we are back up and looking for some developers who are trust worthy and loyal.
First off
Requirements Gotta know java for at least more than 3 years. Must have Skype and able to voice chat at least. Trust and worthy Active
Of course the server is not public or realized yet anywhere. So I and some developers who wish to join will start fixing some glitches that i know adding some stuff.
[size=14pt]This will be a payed job in the future.[/size]
Add me on Skype
Luigi.favilli2
We can talk more!
